    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Helper class to do a scoped lock on a mutex implementing the RAII idiom. Note! this class <emphasis>does not</emphasis> prevent a deadlock in the case when same thread is locking the same mutex twice. </para>
